      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Supporting Context\n\nThis sample is intentionally simple. The home-page template should answer **what this place is** and **where to click first** before it becomes an article.\n\nA small amount of context is useful, but destinations stay primary.",
