      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Step 1: Open The Graph\n\nAction:\n- Open this smoke test graph.\n- Confirm the sample home composition renders on canvas.\n\nResult:\n- [ ] PASS\n- [ ] FAIL",
        "definitionKey": "markdown",
        "_classBinding": {
