      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Step 2: Inspect The Structural Core\n\nAction:\n- Inspect the graph in edit mode.\n- Confirm the structure includes declaration, title, type-definition, one `port` node bound to the `ui-view` class, destination ports, and supporting context.\n\nResult:\n- [ ] PASS\n- [ ] FAIL",
