      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "### Expected\n\nThe scaffold includes:\n- `declaration`\n- `title`\n- `type-definition`\n- one `port` node bound to the `ui-view` class\n- at least two primary destination ports\n- one short supporting-context node",
